1. My sister wants to marry Pete. 2. Follow him. He will show you where the metro
is. 3. He misses his wife a lot. 4. My brother married her about 2 years ago. 5. She
entered the classroom at three sharp. 6. At the end of the street he turned the corner.
7. She divorced him in December. 8. He did not answer my question. 9. Don't enter the
room. 10. If you want, join us. 11. My sister will call Germany tomorrow. 12. Watch me.
13. Do you doubt my words? 14. When did he leave Rome? IS. Don't approach me.
